\c 21
\s Ukubusa kukaJoramu koJuda
\p
\v 1 UJehoshafathi waselala laboyise, wangcwatshelwa kuboyise emzini kaDavida. UJoramu indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\v 2 Njalo wayelabafowabo, amadodana kaJehoshafathi, oAzariya, loJehiyeli, loZekhariya, loAzariya, loMikayeli, loShefathiya. Bonke laba babengamadodana kaJehoshafathi inkosi yakoIsrayeli\x + 21.4. 12.6. 23.2. 24.5,16. 28.19,23,27. 33.18. 35.18.\x*.
\v 3 Uyise wasebanika izipho ezinengi zesiliva lezegolide lezempahla eziligugu\x + Gen. 24.53.\x* kanye lemizi ebiyelweyo koJuda\x + 11.5.\x*; kodwa umbuso wawunika uJehoramu ngoba wayelizibulo.
\v 4 UJehoramu esephakeme embusweni kayise waziqinisa, wabulala bonke abafowabo ngenkemba njalo le\add zinye\add* zeziphathamandla zakoIsrayeli\x + 21.4. 12.6. 23.2. 24.5,16. 28.19,23,27. 33.18. 35.18.\x*.
\p
\v 5 UJehoramu wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amathathu lambili esiba yinkosi, wabusa iminyaka eyisificaminwembili eJerusalema\x + 2 Kho. 8.17-24.\x*.
\v 6 Wasehamba ngendlela yamakhosi akoIsrayeli, njengokwenza kwendlu kaAhabi, ngoba indodakazi kaAhabi yayingumkakhe; wasesenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\x + 18.1.\x*\nd*.
\v 7 Kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* kayithandanga ukuchitha indlu kaDavida ngenxa yesivumelwano eyayisenze loDavida, lanjengoba yayithe izanika yena lamadodana akhe isibane insuku zonke.
\p
\v 8 Ensukwini zakhe uEdoma wahlubuka wasuka phansi kwesandla sakoJuda, basebezibekela inkosi.
\v 9 UJehoramu wasechapha lenduna zakhe lenqola zonke laye, wavuka ebusuku, wawatshaya amaEdoma ayezingelezele yena lenduna zenqola\x + 2 Kho. 8.21.\x*.
\v 10 UEdoma wahlubuka-ke wasuka phansi kwesandla sakoJuda kuze kube lamuhla. Khona iLibhina yahlubuka ngalesosikhathi yasuka phansi kwesandla sakhe, ngoba wayedelile iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu waboyise.
\v 11 Futhi yena wenza indawo eziphakemeyo entabeni zakoJuda, wenza abahlali beJerusalema baphinge\x + 21.13. Eks. 34.16.\x*, waduhisa uJuda\x + 2 Kho. 17.21.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Kwasekufika kuye incwadi ivela kuElija umprofethi isithi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaDavida uyihlo: Ngenxa yokuthi ungahambanga ezindleleni zikaJehoshafathi uyihlo\x + 17.3.\x* lezindleleni zikaAsa inkosi yakoJuda\x + 14.2-5.\x*,
\v 13 kodwa uhambe ngendlela yamakhosi akoIsrayeli\x + 21.6.\x*, wenza uJuda labahlali beJerusalema baphinge\x + 21.13. Eks. 34.16.\x* njengobuwule bendlu kaAhabi\x + 2 Kho. 9.22. 1 Kho. 16.31-33.\x*, futhi-ke ubulele abafowenu bendlu kayihlo\x + 21.4.\x* ababengcono kulawe\x + 1 Kho. 2.32.\x*,
\v 14 khangela, iN\nd kosi\nd* izatshaya ngokutshaya okukhulu ebantwini bakho lebantwaneni bakho lakubomkakho, lakuyo yonke impahla yakho.
\v 15 Lawe uzakuba semikhuhlaneni emikhulu ngesifo samathumbu akho, amathumbu akho aze aphume ngenxa yesifo usuku ngosuku\x + 21.18,19.\x*.
\p
\v 16 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimvusela uJehoramu umoya wamaFilisti lamaArabhiya ayeseceleni kwamaEthiyophiya.
\v 17 Asesenyukela koJuda ayifohlela athumba yonke impahla eyatholakala endlini yenkosi kanye lamadodana ayo labafazi bayo; kakwaze kwasala indodana kuyo ngaphandle kukaJehowahazi, icinathunjana lamadodana ayo.
\p
\v 18 Langemva kwakho konke lokho iN\nd kosi\nd* yamtshaya emathunjini akhe ngomkhuhlane ongelaselapho\x + 21.15.\x*.
\v 19 Kwasekusithi umnyaka ngomnyaka, langesikhathi sokuphuma kokucina kweminyaka emibili, amathumbu akhe aphuma ngomkhuhlane wakhe; ngakho wafa ngemikhuhlane emibi\x + Gen. 24.55.\x*. Kodwa abantu bakhe kabambaselanga umlilo njengomlilo waboyise\x + 16.14. 1 Sam. 31.12.\x*.
\v 20 Wayele\add minyaka\add* engamatshumi amathathu lambili esiba yinkosi, wabusa iminyaka eyisificaminwembili eJerusalema; wahamba engaloyiseki\x + 21.5. 2 Kho. 8.17,24.\x*. Basebemngcwabela emzini kaDavida, kodwa hatshi emangcwabeni amakhosi\x + 24.25. 28.27. Jer. 22.18.\x*.
